# CI 临时写出（基线见 data/telemetry-snapshots/<date>/，须提交）
data/telemetry-snapshots/ci-current/
data/cognitive-telemetry-snapshots/ci-current/
data/pagination-telemetry-snapshots/ci-current/
data/negotiation-telemetry-snapshots/ci-current/
